OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774023076
OL,3,CGerry Adams in London 'to assert the
OL,4,Clegitimacy of the republican cause'
OL,6,FIn a statement, he said: "Had the
OL,7,Fdefendant not been the senior figure
OL,8,Fin the IRA that he was, there would
OL,9,Fhave been absolutely no point in the
OL,10,FBritish, Irish and United States
OL,11,Fgovernments dealing with him the way
OL,12,Fthey did on the road to the Good
OL,13,FFriday Agreement in 1998."
OL,15,FMs Studd said on Thursday: "In order
OL,16,Fto establish his role in the Army
OL,17,FCouncil in the 1990s, we have had to
OL,18,Fset the ground for why it is that his
OL,19,Faccount is not plausible."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUuD@ZO]wD@\OU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
